q 0 G 1 w 40 600 m 392 600 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 578 Td (ADHD doesn't just affect the person who has it - it affects the) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 563 Td (relationship dynamic. Understanding this is the first step to healing.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 548 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 533 Td (COMMON PATTERNS IN ADHD RELATIONSHIPS:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 518 Td (- Parent-child dynamic \(non-ADHD partner becomes 'nagging parent'\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 503 Td (- Hyperfocus courtship -> neglect \(intense beginning, then distracted\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 488 Td (- Broken promises \(not from lack of caring, but lack of follow-through\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 473 Td (- Emotional volatility \(dysregulation affects both partners\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 458 Td (- Unequal mental load \(one partner carries all the planning\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 443 Td (- Communication breakdowns \(distraction during conversations\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 428 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 413 Td (WHAT'S HAPPENING \(not excuses, but explanations\):) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 398 Td (- Working memory issues: forget requests, lose track of conversations) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 383 Td (- Time blindness: chronically late, poor time estimation) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 368 Td (- Executive dysfunction: sees the mess but can't initiate cleaning) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 353 Td (- Emotional dysregulation: overreacts, can't let things go) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 338 Td (- Dopamine-seeking: novelty preference affects attention to partner) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 323 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 308 Td (THE GOOD NEWS:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 293 Td (- Understanding WHY eliminates blame and builds compassion) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 278 Td (- Systems \(not willpower\) solve most ADHD relationship issues) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 263 Td (- Many ADHD traits are ASSETS: creativity, humor, passion, energy) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 248 Td (- Both partners have legitimate needs that CAN be met) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
