BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 578 Td (PATTERN 1: The Nag Cycle) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 563 Td (Partner A asks -> Partner B forgets -> A asks again -> B feels) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 548 Td (nagged -> A feels unheard -> both resentful) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 533 Td (BREAK IT: Use shared reminders/apps, not verbal requests) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 518 Td () Tj ET
