BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 488 Td (A criticizes -> B gets overwhelmed -> B shuts down/walks away ->) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 473 Td (A feels abandoned -> A escalates -> B shuts down more) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 458 Td (BREAK IT: Scheduled check-ins, time-outs with return time) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 443 Td () Tj ET
