BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 413 Td (Something goes wrong -> A blames ADHD -> B says 'it's not an) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 398 Td (excuse' -> A feels shame -> A gets defensive -> fight) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 383 Td (BREAK IT: 'The ADHD made this harder AND I'm responsible') Tj ET
