BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 443 Td (FOR THE NON-ADHD PARTNER:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 428 Td (- Their reaction is not proportional - that's the ADHD, not you) Tj ET
