BT 0 g /F2 13 Tf 125.52000000000001 610 Td (REJECTION SENSITIVE DYSPHORIA) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 40 600 m 392 600 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 578 Td (RSD is intense emotional pain triggered by perceived rejection) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 563 Td (or criticism. It affects 99% of people with ADHD.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 548 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 533 Td (WHAT RSD LOOKS LIKE IN RELATIONSHIPS:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 518 Td (- Overreacting to mild criticism or suggestions) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 503 Td (- Assuming partner is disappointed/angry without evidence) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 488 Td (- People-pleasing to avoid any possibility of rejection) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 473 Td (- Withdrawing or rage in response to feeling criticized) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 458 Td (- Interpreting neutral facial expressions as negative) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 443 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 428 Td (FOR THE ADHD PARTNER - WHEN RSD HITS:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 413 Td (1. Name it: 'This might be RSD talking, not reality') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 398 Td (2. Ask: 'Are you actually upset with me or am I reading into this?') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 383 Td (3. Wait before reacting \(give it 20 minutes\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 368 Td (4. Check the facts, not the feelings) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 353 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 338 Td (FOR THE NON-ADHD PARTNER - HOW TO HELP:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 323 Td (1. Lead with reassurance: 'I love you AND I need to discuss...') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 308 Td (2. Be specific, not general \('this dish' not 'you never clean'\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 293 Td (3. Separate the person from the behavior) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 278 Td (4. When they spiral: 'I'm not rejecting you. I'm addressing this thing.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 263 Td () Tj ET
